    • Enum Constant Detail

      • WALL

        public static final CellType WALL
        Cell type for walls. You can't step on walls, and they're black squares.

      • EMPTY

        public static final CellType EMPTY
        Cell type for empty cells. You can walk/step on them, but only one time. They're white squares.

      • START

        public static final CellType START
        Cell type for start cell. You start from this cell. It is white square with green triangle inside.

      • FINISH

        public static final CellType FINISH
        Cell type for finish cell. If you have stepped on all empty cells and then step on this one, level is completed.

      • BACKGROUND_SQUARE

        public static final CellType BACKGROUND_SQUARE
        Cell type for background squares. This cells are fully equal to walls, but method BackgroundSquare.draw(int, int, GraphicsContext, GamePlayController) clears rectangle and doesn't draw anything.
